
### Privacy Policy for Reserve GH

Last updated: 19th Dec 2024

Introduction:
Welcome to Reserve GH. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide while using our mobile application, available on Apple Store and Google Play Store. By using Reserve GH, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection and Use:
We collect the following information for the effective operation of our service:

- Phone Number: Essential for account creation and verification. It is unique to each user and restaurant owner and cannot be modified.
- Restaurant Information (For Restaurant Owners): Includes restaurant location, images, name, keywords, and food types. This information is used to showcase restaurants to users.
- Location Data (For Users): We request your location data to show nearby restaurants. You may decline to provide this, but it may limit certain functionalities of the app.

Account Management:
- Edit Information: Users and restaurant owners can edit their information, except for their phone numbers.
- Account Deletion: You can delete your account at your discretion.
- Notifications: Users will receive notifications about new restaurants and booking statuses.

Data Storage and Security:
- The information collected is stored securely and is used solely for the purpose of providing and improving our service. We do not share your data with any third parties.
- We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information.

User Rights:
- You have the right to access, update, or delete the information we have on you.
- You can exercise these rights by logging into your account or contacting us at reserve.ghana23@gmail.com.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:
- We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at reserve.ghana23@gmail.com.

